rows.label: qst660115_msg0001
rows.name:
Hello, dear everyone.
How is mood today?

rows.label: qst660115_msg0002
rows.name:
I but humble orderly of most honorable
Sir Orderly of most highly exalted
Master Nopon Archsage.

rows.label: qst660115_msg0003
rows.name:
Has reached my attention that Master
Archsage go and issue new batch of
Noponstone into circulation...

rows.label: qst660115_msg0004
rows.name:
From there, Sir Orderly go into tizzy
overdrive to prepare new wares to
trade back for Noponstone with friends.

rows.label: qst660115_msg0005
rows.name:
And therefore, I get roped in to help
with manual labor side. Sigh.

rows.label: qst660115_msg0006
rows.name:
But after long service in warehouse,
I now get promotion! New duty is swap
Noponstone for Flawless Noponstone!

rows.label: qst660115_msg0007
rows.name:
If find pockets overflowing with plain
Noponstone, please to consider change
into higher denomination!
